publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-3874 Mr David Davidson: Scottish Parliament Election Process—That the Parliament welcomes the certainty resulting from the statement in the House of Commons on 24 January 2006 by the Secretary of State for Scotland that there will be no changes to the election process ahead of the Scottish Parliament elections in 2007.

S2M-3874 Scottish Parliament Election Process (lodged on 25 January 2006) John Swinburne*
